span></strong></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">注意：来校前请及时联系，避免路线、位置</span></strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\">导航</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\">错误&nbsp;或 被他人冒充诱导！</strong></p>', 'admin', '0', '1524205051');
INSERT INTO `think_single` VALUES ('26', '47', '来往路线', '', '', '', '', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">第一次来校可安排到车站接（方便情况下</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">机场1：114路→火车站&nbsp;转&nbsp;地铁2号线→望城坡（汽车西站）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">机场2：机场快巴<span style=\"font-size: 18px; list-style-type: none; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">→汽车西站</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; line-height: inherit; text-indent: 2em; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">火车站1：地铁2号线→望城坡（汽车西站）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">火车站2：12路公交→汽车西站&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">高铁站（火车南站）：地铁2号线→望城坡（汽车西站）</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); text-indent: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">汽车东站1: 168路公交→汽车西站</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">汽车东站2:中巴车→汽车西站</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 24px; color: rgb(29, 27, 16); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">汽车南站: 17路公交或坐班车 → 汽车西站</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">汽车北站: 149路公交或者班车 →&nbsp;汽车西站</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 15px; padding: 0px; list-style-type: none; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 12px; line-height: 24px; font-family: 宋体; vertical-align: baseline; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(65, 65, 65); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">汽车西站：坐班车或公交车 到望城乔口镇（励志学校）</span></p>', 'admin', '0', '1523415983');
INSERT INTO `think_single` VALUES ('27', '48', '交通地图', '', '', '', '', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/uploads/image/20180117/1516168718299888.jpg\" title=\"1516168718299888.jpg\" alt=\"地图.jpg\" width=\"532\" height=\"318\" style=\"width: 532px; height: 318px;\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe class=\"ueditor_baidumap\" src=\"http://www.qsn580.com/Ueditor/dialogs/map/show.html#center=112.922516,28.219808&zoom=14&width=530&height=340&markers=112.923235,28.210259&markerStyles=l,A\" frameborder=\"0\" width=\"534\" height=\"344\"></iframe></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">学校地址：湖南省长沙市乔口卫生院附近<br/></span></strong></span></p>', 'admin', '0', '1519951836');
INSERT INTO `think_single` VALUES ('29', '32', '教学特色', '', '', '', '', '<center style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">一、远程监控，透明管教&nbsp;</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span></strong><br/></center><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">我校是全国首家启用现代化高清网络远程监控教学管理系统。24小时面对所有在校学生家长开放，无死角视察孩子在校情况。手机电脑随时随地一览无余，看着孩子在成长！</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">二、杜决打骂，禁止体罚&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">是全国首家实施人性化和谐式教育，提倡心理认知教育，杜绝打骂、禁止体罚。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">三、师资雄厚，专家治学&nbsp;</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 20px;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;\">★★★★★</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;学校有专业心理老师及专家住校治学辅导，设有一对一和多对一的专业针对性心理辅导方案，让每一位孩子的问题得到快速辅导和化解，确保孩子的转变效果，为您解忧！</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">四、</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">分类分校，<strong>因材施教&nbsp;</strong></span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">★★★★★</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\">学校设有三大校区：戒毒心理辅导中心、强制行为矫正中心、综合励志心理辅导中心。各个校区按学生不同类别问题再次进行分类分层辅导及管理，避免不同问题的交叉感染，从而达到因材施教，分类辅导效果，快速根除孩子不良问题。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">五、签订协议，保证效果&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">★★★★★</span></strong></span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">报名入校我们将签订教育委托协议书，保证孩子在校的安全和教育辅导效果（包含：双方责任、相关费用、孩子安全、教育方案、辅导效果、后期服务等等一式两份的法律协议文书）。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">六、</span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">心理辅导，文化补习</span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;<strong style=\"text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">★★★★★</span></strong></span></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong style=\"text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"></span></strong>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp; 根据人的功能原理，心理思想是人的行为指令中枢，一切的不良语言与行动行为将是受到心理思想的不良反应所导致。因为我校抓住了根基，以心理辅导和思想引导为主，根除不良问题，指标又治本，安全有效。同时为了避免影响孩子的学习进度，实施文化补习辅导，加强和提升文化学习水平，与教育成长同步。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">七、同吃同住，学习无忧&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong style=\"text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">★★★★★</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">老师专家24小时与学生同吃同住、同学同乐、随时辅导的VIP教育学校。让学生有问题得解决，有困难有帮助，有需要有老师的人性化教育教育方针，不论是问题教育还是文化学习，随时随地开课，处处是健康与成长。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">八、亲子互动，随时沟通&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong style=\"text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">★★★★★</span></strong></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">家长</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">可以</span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">随时随地视察到孩子的在校情况，也可以随时来校看望，并随时都可以跟孩子保持联系沟通，促进家庭和谐，增强亲子感情。亲子互动，沟通无限!</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">九、兴趣培养，提升技能&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong style=\"text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">★★★★★</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">通过相关心理测试和对学生的了解，发掘学生的潜力，培养其兴趣爱好，提升相关技术技能。同时可根据其特长爱好学习相关专业技能技术，并参加学校的相关专业技能知识考试合格可频发相关专业技能证书（国家认可，全国通用）。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">十、一人转变，全家幸福&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong style=\"text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">★★★★★</span></strong></span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\"><strong style=\"text-align: -webkit-center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"></span></strong></span></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); font-size: 18px;\">问题孩子的问题，并非是孩子一个人的问题，而是一个家庭甚至是一个家族的问题。每一位孩子都是家庭的未来，是不可切断的命脉。只有孩子健康成长，才能拥有一个幸福的家庭！</span></p>', '教育服务中心', '0', '1458487275');
